Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,↑Title↑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙从以前开始就容易招来灾祸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近来如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.60,0:02:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟我约会喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那家伙搞什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么就走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你怎么了嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.50,0:02:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.50,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然随便跑到学校来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫我怎么跟大家解释啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话不就好了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能说得出口啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.70,0:02:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么我们一起消灭吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在怀疑我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种案件又发生了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是你想说Nero没死？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来别人说的话你都没在听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说过我讨厌血吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何况Nero有吸血吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.30,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.90,0:03:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样就说清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  竟然怀疑到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  Nero是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙不过是个刺客
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.10,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺客？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.50,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是我要找的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望志贵…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我也帮忙找  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就今晚九点在公园见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.80,0:05:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要出去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对志贵少爷来说是很重要的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个请您拿去用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是正门以及入口的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为志贵少爷是我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  翡翠小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我翡翠就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不直接叫名字的话我会很不自在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我出去了  翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上请小心  志贵少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虚空之蛇？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人这么称呼Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个什么样的家伙？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roa为了追求永远生命的极限
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃了对肉体的执着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙会转生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.40,0:06:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转生？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对Roa来说  肉体只不过是个容器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不断更换容器之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已经反覆转生18次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是没完没了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在他转生成什么样的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他发现我到了这个城市把气息隐藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你打算怎么找啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的眼睛看那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消  消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是“死者”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被Roa吸过血的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是Roa的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙一面重复吸血行为一面增加自己的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把那些血供应Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要继续这样猎杀死者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一定会有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想把他逼出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.90,0:09:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么突然想帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.60,0:09:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你不是非常不愿意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说到现在我还是不想牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么要帮我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是因为痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.10,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为弓冢被卷入事件当中的时候我觉得很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她是朋友又对我有种莫名的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是志贵的话说不定能打倒Roa
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是连你都觉得难缠的对手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对自己的评价太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你对我的评价过高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡眠不足吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜不睡觉在做些什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡扯什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有漂亮女朋友的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都说了  她不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.80,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.20,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝杯茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正规啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说我也是茶道社的社长嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.60,0:12:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是社长  其实社员只有我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一杯粗茶不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.40,0:12:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么突然请我喝茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.40,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远野  你是不是有什么烦恼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近都没什么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:13:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便说给我听的话  可以找我谈谈喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为那个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天来学校的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是那种完全不考虑别人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既任性又自我中心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后把人推下地狱的类型
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐你…认识她吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.20,0:14:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的个性就是无法放着像远野你这样的人不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚刚…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是邀请我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说要跟我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫作搭讪  对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为突然跟我说话我还以为是敌人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很危险啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚说了什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.80,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Roa吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说电动游乐场吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电动游乐场？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到志贵这么笨手笨脚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接下来去这里玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.60,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常这个时间不会营业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.83,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(近期上映)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  一直做这种事真的没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前都没有发现任何气息应该没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不但白天可以在外面走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会去电动游乐场玩  还要我带你去电影院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵被既有概念影响太深了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前不巧没有当吸血鬼的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天算我请你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.50,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！ 这样好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逞强喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的  交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们再去喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.80,0:17:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.80,0:17:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:17:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利者必须要同情战败者才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位总共是2352圆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.20,0:18:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志贵  等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管  快点走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.50,0:18:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚刚做的事情可是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不够用所以复制一下而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是犯罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.70,0:18:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  你就算不做这种事就已经够引人注目了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是说这都是我的错？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.90,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  要找Roa的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不要太引人注目不是比较好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不是很认同  但是志贵这样说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是在哪个地方割到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为走得很匆忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什么严重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.20,0:19:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arcueid Brunestud
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ciel  你又想被我杀死吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被远野杀死时的伤还没完全好的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法做得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我到底有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在的目的应该跟我一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就给我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太碍眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:20:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能看着远野遇到危险
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.80,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事志贵已经同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.50,0:21:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对他来说最危险的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你这八百年来的自我压抑我表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  那也到达极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以反抗本能的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.80,0:21:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果远野出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会解决掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着
